@TravisEz13 @iSazonov @adityapatwardhan @SydneyhSmith We can make a post-release workflow which can auto-generate PRs on [microsoft/winget-pkgs](https://github.com/microsoft/winget-pkgs) using a github personal access token (PAT) from any maintainers' account or some bot like @PoshChan.

Store submission can be performed using https://github.com/marketplace/actions/microsoft-store-publish.

